&+R13/10/06&n
- Removed a mob from Bahamut's Palace that was being dimmed to in order to
  cheese the zone.
- Players who have followed the path of the multiclass, but then have decided
  to return to the simple life, can now pray to the gods of Duris at the Altar
  of the &+RMadMaN&n in the center of the &+WLost Temple of &+GTikitzopl&n. 
  Doing so requires an epic skillpoint.
