  checks. Changed to a bonus modifier instead of insta-success.

&+R09/10/06&n
- The news is now correctly updated on the website.

&+R05/10/06&n
- Lowered move drain while running from pvp fights, a tad.
- Casters get a few extra spellslots to compensate for everyone having extra 
  hitpoints.
- Rogues now ignore the move penalty for the first few seconds after a flee,
  giving them a chance to get back to the battle and stab!

&+R05/10/06&n
  &+YBig Changes&n
- Adjusted the hps changes, so they a little less drastic. Lowered
  the affect of damroll generaly so you get less extra damage / damroll you get.
  Lowered the bonus for damroll and hitroll / level bonus a bit.

- Base hitpoints for players has been dramatically increased.
- All players now receive a major level dependant hit/dam bonus.
- Mobs will now deal more damage to players.
- After engaging in pvp, your moves will decrease while you move much faster 
  until you calm down.

  The purpose of these changes is to reduce dependency on hit/dam/hp equipment, 
  so that you can fill those slots with more appropriate +stat gear. It will 
  also hopefully lead to longer and more interesting battles, and the movement 
  code should prevent people from running away too easily. As with everything, 
  we will be monitoring this change and will be adjusting accordingly.

&+R29/09/06&n
- Evil races can now see a few squares on the map during the day.
- Magical darkness should no longer blind goodies.
- Goodies should now be able to see better in the UD.
- If you notice anything funky about this, &+YDON'T PANIC&n, please
  just report it and we will get it fixed ASAP.

&+R14/09/06&n
